---
interface Props {
  lang?: 'en' | 'es';
}

const { lang = 'en' } = Astro.props;

// Define content based on language
const content = lang === 'es' ? {
  aboutTitle: "Sobre nosotros",
  aboutText: [
    "Somos abogados colombianos - abogados -. Entendemos la cultura, el idioma y las prácticas comunes del sistema legal colombiano.",
    "Hemos practicado la Ley en diferentes áreas obteniendo valiosas perspectivas para proteger tus intereses.",
    "Nuestra filosofía es simplificar las complejidades del mundo legal y priorizar la comunicación abierta, la confianza y el aspecto humano de todas nuestras interacciones."
  ],
  missionTitle: "Misión y Visión",
  missionText: [
    "Queremos ayudar a expatriados, nómadas y viajeros con sus procesos legales en Colombia porque sabemos lo que significa jugar lejos de casa.",
    "En última instancia, queremos enriquecer Colombia a través del intercambio cultural, porque la cultura solo se enriquece con expatriados, extranjeros, viajeros y nómadas.",
    "¡Damos la bienvenida a los expatriados! Entendemos que las diferencias culturales y las barreras del idioma pueden ralentizar algunos procesos legales [ya lentos]."
  ]
} : {
  aboutTitle: "About us",
  aboutText: [
    "We are Colombian attorneys - abogados -. We understand the culture, language and common practices of the Colombian legal system.",
    "We have practiced the Law across different areas gaining valuable insights to protect your interests.",
    "Our philosophy is to simplify the complexities of the legal world and prioritize open communication, trust, and the human aspect of all our interactions."
  ],
  missionTitle: "Mission and Vision",
  missionText: [
    "We want to help expats, nomads and travelers with their legal processes in Colombia because we know what it means to play away from home.",
    "Ultimately, we want enrich Colombia through cultural exchange, because culture gets only richer with expats, foreigners, travelers, and nomads.",
    "We welcome expats! We understand cultural differences and language barriers can slower down some [already slow] legal processes."
  ]
};
---
       
<section class="h-auto pt-16 my-16 md:my-6 max-w-screen-xl mx-auto ">
       <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:gap-6">
              <div class="w-full md:w-2/3 bg-slate-100 p-4 rounded rounded-lg shadow">
                     <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">
                            {content.aboutTitle}
                     </div>                 
                     <div class="text-lg text-primary">
                            {content.aboutText.map((text) => (
                              <p class="mb-4 font-light p-3 bg-white rounded">{text}</p>
                            ))}
                     </div>
              </div>
              <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 bg-slate-100 p-4 shadow rounded rounded-lg">
                     <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">
                            {content.missionTitle}
                     </div>   
                     <div class="text-lg font-light text-primary">
                            {content.missionText.map((text) => (
                              <p class="mb-4">{text}</p>
                            ))}
                     </div>                     
              </div>
       </div>       
</section> 